metadata.name: Sweet Puppy Girl
metadata.description:
"Sweet Puppy Girl"
The dearest little puppy girl.
She is the youngest sister in three.
You will be the best friend for her.
She gives you a big smile and healing.

This is the first collection of Foundation.
I decided to use the advantage of digital art, so that I decided to make animation.
It took over 100 hours to make this art.
I hope owner will enjoy to decorate this art in own musium.
